    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富裕纳税人短缺迫使加州冻结支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/california-orders-spending-freeze-on-68-billion-budget-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆 (Gavin Newsom) 下令冻结支出，因为该州下一财年的预算赤字预计将飙升至 680 亿美元——几乎比最初预测高出五倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/california-orders-spending-freeze-on-68-billion-budget-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 22:38:05 GMT</pubDate>
